comnickdchee.github.a3am.Models

Class Exchange

  • java.lang.Object
    • comnickdchee.github.a3am.Models.Exchange

  • public class Exchange
extends java.lang.Object
    Exchange class which keeps track of exchanges between a specific book between 2 users. This is created whenever a request is accepted by an owner of a book.
